===Noun===
'''Kannada'''

# Kannada is the State Language of Southern State, Karnataka, in South [[India]]. It's spoken by over 5 Million people worldwide. It's used in the states of [[Karnataka]], [[Andhra Pradesh]], [[Tamil Nadu]], [[Maharashtra]]. It uses Kannada Script.

